Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so unusual of you to pay us a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sorta kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you need something from uncle and aunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need anything in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are both coming late \Nfrom school retraining courses{no fucking clue what 学校の研修会 is} today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Busy as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come again some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cooking the dinner today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll eat with us, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know if I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:03:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good, all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't been hanging out as siblings in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since he started playing pachislot, \NGinya changed completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He became anxious, sorrowful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oblivious to the very concept of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If it goes on this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya would only stray further away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if you leave early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In your opinion, \Nwhat do I look like to men?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, you think it's all cool \Nto leave me stood up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what bothers you? Yuri, you found some bozo \Nwho dared to leave you stood up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be that time with Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing of the kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \NI remember Ginya repenting that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he is very sorry for what he did to Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was an open-hearted apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I just have no luck with men.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe I should really rethink Ginya's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what did you want from our piblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your dad's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to everyone's care, \Nlooking better already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Something... happened to uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,While moving stones in the garden the other day, \Noverstrained his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He was alright, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Recovered already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:04:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, isn't it Gin? \NIt's been a truly long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you went to Tokyo University. \NIt's great to see you're doing all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't worry your dad and mom \Nby spending so much time playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still pickling out pickles, \Nbut maybe you want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad can't live without those pickles lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya did not show up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya knows he is allowed to practice in Slothium \Nfor promotion to Knight games and higher, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is adumbrated in the match date notification, explicitly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is his first title challenging game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you run off to, Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I hoped to find him here \Nafter failing to do so in parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be in condition to win if you don't prepare?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Attaway, attaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My luck is improving steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is so splendid about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I nullified the series of Riichi Eyes \Nby a following Renchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What an eccentric way of pressing buttons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To peek at someone's practice, \Nyou need a ticket you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really mean to peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just impressed by your manner of pressing. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're much nicer{/ prettier} a guy \Nthan what rumors say, Oumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing my fortune-telling can't figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fortune-telling...{\i0} \NThen, you must be that guy, Occult Kanpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you mind not calling me \Nby that nickname anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okajima Kanpei \Nis my more commonly used name, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Relying solely on jinx and fortune-telling, \Nyou always put up quite a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Remained undefeated for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel that tomorrow \NI'll be in perfect shape as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stars aligned and my biorhythm is steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My tomorrow's opponent \Nis doomed to just serve me a foil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,An unfortunate fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Had you been my opponent, \Nyou'd think just losing is a favorable option.{/ you'd prefer to just let me defeat you altogether.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where and what are you up to, Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:49.23,Song,,0,0,0,,New shop opens at 7/5 \NFrom 2 dresses - sale
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you never told me what you came here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, there's nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We both know it can't be nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You came all the way home after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Don't tell me. \NNot like it matters now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Suppose dad is still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He can go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wanna see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For me it's opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fibber.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand it like no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No use fooling me, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The time we ran off from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if we already have dad and mom here, \Nwhy do you wanna go look for dad elsewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I'm looking for \Nis yours and mine true father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}True father?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But didn't he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Our true father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what mom said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare crying! \NStop crying I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to cry then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I still remember how firmly we were scolded after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, you didn't ever drop another word \Nabout our real father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as for the current us, \Nwe already have dad and mom, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just our Otonashi uncle and aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop putting it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I talk to you, \Nyou seem to need to point that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to have a brother \Nthat keeps denigrating them like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Think and look for yourself, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Both me and you ended up here \Nbecause of our pops!{Lit: Because we had father, we are here - I don't really see what's that supposed to mean}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times you call your aunt "mother!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,For how longer will you keep saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making me worry about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't they caring enough for you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He was duly punished for abandoning you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He died soon as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In case our true father really is \Nstill alive and well and you get to meet him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,brother, what are you going to tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:11:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to tell him \Nall your grudges for abandoning us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That is quite
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong.{/ Not about that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro... Brother, I'm speaking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Got carried away earlier. \NWill you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be one saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you folding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kojiro used to fold them for you every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey... \N- Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person our true father is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta be a mighty kind fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you wanna go meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But didn't he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom said he is dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call her mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But mom is mom, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Mai would rather wanna return home now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Father really is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was entering high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom decided it's time to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She said we should rather forget \Nabout how she told us he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you keep it until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm your sister after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how my brother feels\Nand try to be mindful of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, had I known that, \NI'd not give up back in those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed easily to get over father and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But in your heart, \Nhis place is probably much more deep-seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:13:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When you dropped out of university halfway through,\Ndad and mom told me this:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Eventually, we failed to become a family for Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We fed you those lies \Nto help you forget that man sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But perhaps, he returned to Ginya's heart, \Nhurting him only the more."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You really wouldn't want the truth about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please understand, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But after seeing you today,\NI think there's more to it than just an old grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go meet him. \NI don't mind now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}should{\i0} meet him, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You've...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,grown up so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm 17 already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have long buried the child in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Buried the child?! \NDon't you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I didn't do anything of the kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dumb as nails, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then. \NWe'd better be heading back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Lest I'll not be able to prepare dinner in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry the shopping bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as the one the principal{/ director / head physician} folded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't even eat with us before returning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I got to hang out with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to this, tomorrow \NI'll be fighting with a clear mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So self-willed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fighting?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you going to be fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi you say? \NWe'll see if he's in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm told Occult Kanpei \Nhas his luck in zenith today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, this should be \Nthe first interesting match in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, we proceed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Knight's title challenging bout.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Going already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's match I should, \Nby all means, see with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just the today's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That Otonashi Ginya \Nseems to always be on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though you fell in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? \NWon't even answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I am forever in your debt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not something you'd expect Ryo to say.{/ You don't sound like Ryo at all.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo. Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo... Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In the title challenging bout, one side is the defender, \Nand the other is the challenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It is decided{guess} by a one-on-one battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, participants are invited to pick a machine{guess}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, this seat is reserved for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My compass pointed to it, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lucky colors are \Nred and purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky item is... snakeskin wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know how it may help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time without Kanpei's occult gimmicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:39.29,Song,,0,0,0,,Time limit for this bout: 2 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always exciting to see, \Nwhich kind of occultery he uses this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A multiplier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't align your target \Nwith the Bar Wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bar Wind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For the moment, \NBar Wind blows towards the Small Factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No wind is blowing \Ntowards Big Factors now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore I only aim for Small Factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know no shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't even heed humbly to someone's advice, \Ncalling them stupid instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, how about I prove it \Nwith the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll win the next one my own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no one is telling me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My, is that so? \NWell, I did my best to teach you some wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why does he press it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I press "Max Bet" 3 times, \Nbecause I have a hunch it's a lucky number{/ because it gives me the sense of coming success}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Occult Battling Style \Nseems to pay off splendidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya keeps making a fool of himself because of Occult Battling Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He cannot press the buttons his usual way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I would never believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Riichi Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, seeking{guess} Riichi Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Watch and learn!{guess; maybe "Found it!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bar Wind changed it's direction. Then, I'll alter my aim as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From Small Factors, \NI'm realigning it to Riichi Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this a Riichi Eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Red on the right, gold on the left - \Nthe omen of Big!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be fighting like this all day long!{Lit: Fight for 24 hours? - I have no fucking clue what this means}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time \NI'm seeing that kind of Riichi Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Riichi Eyes \Nonly this guy hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Secured! Renchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Catching your breath after establishing a Renchan? \NRenchans expire, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can decide for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We decide nothing. \NEverything in Destiny's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Destiny?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30}The Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did my Renchan streak break?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Told ya -
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Fate's play. \NYou can't go against the Fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You say everything is in Fate's hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So it decided I should lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,After that exhausting battle of pressing buttons \NDaiba spent with me, I have to lose? Here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Remaining time: 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You shittin' me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To honor Daiba's effort, \NI cannot afford to lose yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fate is already beyond salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Riichi Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just some death throes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can catch as many Riichi Eyes as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a Big, it's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullshit! That shouldn't be possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Remaining time: 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fate has already been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That Fate guy \Ndoesn't decide shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You carve your own way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You took the rose-tinted glasses off my eyes!{Lit: The scales fell off my eyes. - idiom means "realize one's wrongdoing" and that's the best way I could tie it up in english; maybe "my eyes are no longer covered by wool"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Game is concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Winner - Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, with this game, \NMr. Otonashi is getting promoted to the Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Secured it! \NFrom now on, I'm one step closer to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.43,0:22:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Paper plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.07,0:22:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.22,0:22:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Backbone.
